---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Real Investor Profiles - Get Global Yields" description="Explore real-world profiles showing how international investors from different countries access US markets, choose brokers, and build portfolios.">
  <section class="w-full px-4 pt-10 pb-14 sm:px-6 sm:pt-12 sm:pb-16 lg:px-8 lg:pt-14 lg:pb-20">
    <div class="investor-profiles-container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="icon-circle">
          <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.982 18.725A7.488 7.488 0 0012 15.75a7.488 7.488 0 00-5.982 2.975m11.963 0a9 9 0 10-11.963 0m11.963 0A8.966 8.966 0 0112 21a8.966 8.966 0 01-5.982-2.275M15 9.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1>Real <span>Investor</span> Profiles</h1>
        <p>See how international investors like you are building wealth in US markets.</p>
        <div class="demo-notice">
          <span class="dot"></span>
          Demo data - real profiles coming soon
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="profiles-grid">
        <div class="profile-card accent-green">
          <div class="card-header">
            <img src="https://flagcdn.com/32x24/ar.png" alt="Argentina" style="width:32px;height:24px;border-radius:3px;">
            <div class="name-block">
              <div class="name">Maria</div>
              <div class="meta">Argentina <span class="separator">|</span> Graphic Designer</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Monthly Investment</span>
            <span class="info-value highlight">$300</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Broker</span>
            <span class="info-value">Interactive Brokers</span>
          </div>
          <div class="allocation">
            <strong>Portfolio:</strong> 60% VOO &nbsp;|&nbsp; 25% SCHD &nbsp;|&nbsp; 15% Cash
          </div>
          <div class="quote">
            <span class="quote-text">I started with just $100 a month. IBKR's low fees made it possible to grow without losing half my returns to commissions.</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="profile-card accent-blue">
          <div class="card-header">
            <img src="https://flagcdn.com/32x24/jp.png" alt="Japan" style="width:32px;height:24px;border-radius:3px;">
            <div class="name-block">
              <div class="name">Kenji</div>
              <div class="meta">Japan <span class="separator">|</span> Software Engineer</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Monthly Investment</span>
            <span class="info-value highlight">$2,000</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Broker</span>
            <span class="info-value">Firstrade</span>
          </div>
          <div class="allocation">
            <strong>Portfolio:</strong> 50% QQQ &nbsp;|&nbsp; 30% VTI &nbsp;|&nbsp; 10% TQQQ &nbsp;|&nbsp; 10% Cash
          </div>
          <div class="quote">
            <span class="quote-text">Living in Tokyo, I thought US markets were out of reach. Firstrade's zero-commission model changed everything for me.</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="profile-card accent-purple">
          <div class="card-header">
            <img src="https://flagcdn.com/32x24/ae.png" alt="UAE" style="width:32px;height:24px;border-radius:3px;">
            <div class="name-block">
              <div class="name">Fatima</div>
              <div class="meta">UAE <span class="separator">|</span> Marketing Director</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Monthly Investment</span>
            <span class="info-value highlight">$5,000</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Broker</span>
            <span class="info-value">Saxo Bank</span>
          </div>
          <div class="allocation">
            <strong>Portfolio:</strong> 40% VWRA &nbsp;|&nbsp; 30% IUIT &nbsp;|&nbsp; 20% AGGU &nbsp;|&nbsp; 10% Cash
          </div>
          <div class="quote">
            <span class="quote-text">As an expat in Dubai, I needed a broker that understood my tax situation. Saxo's W-8BEN handling saved me from the 30% withholding trap.</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="profile-card accent-orange">
          <div class="card-header">
            <img src="https://flagcdn.com/32x24/mx.png" alt="Mexico" style="width:32px;height:24px;border-radius:3px;">
            <div class="name-block">
              <div class="name">Carlos</div>
              <div class="meta">Mexico <span class="separator">|</span> University Professor</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Monthly Investment</span>
            <span class="info-value highlight">$450</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Broker</span>
            <span class="info-value">tastytrade</span>
          </div>
          <div class="allocation">
            <strong>Portfolio:</strong> 45% SPY &nbsp;|&nbsp; 30% QQQ &nbsp;|&nbsp; 15% Covered Call ETFs &nbsp;|&nbsp; 10% Cash
          </div>
          <div class="quote">
            <span class="quote-text">I sell covered calls on SPY every month. tastytrade's options tools are incredible, and the $1 commission per contract is the best I've found.</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="profile-card accent-pink">
          <div class="card-header">
            <img src="https://flagcdn.com/32x24/in.png" alt="India" style="width:32px;height:24px;border-radius:3px;">
            <div class="name-block">
              <div class="name">Ananya</div>
              <div class="meta">India <span class="separator">|</span> Data Analyst</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Monthly Investment</span>
            <span class="info-value highlight">$800</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Broker</span>
            <span class="info-value">Interactive Brokers</span>
          </div>
          <div class="allocation">
            <strong>Portfolio:</strong> 55% VTI &nbsp;|&nbsp; 25% VXUS &nbsp;|&nbsp; 10% BND &nbsp;|&nbsp; 10% Cash
          </div>
          <div class="quote">
            <span class="quote-text">The W-8BEN process seemed intimidating at first, but IBKR's guided form made it simple. Now I get the 15% treaty rate automatically.</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="profile-card accent-teal">
          <div class="card-header">
            <img src="https://flagcdn.com/32x24/de.png" alt="Germany" style="width:32px;height:24px;border-radius:3px;">
            <div class="name-block">
              <div class="name">Lars</div>
              <div class="meta">Germany <span class="separator">|</span> Mechanical Engineer</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Monthly Investment</span>
            <span class="info-value highlight">EUR 1,200</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Broker</span>
            <span class="info-value">DEGIRO</span>
          </div>
          <div class="allocation">
            <strong>Portfolio:</strong> 50% VWCE &nbsp;|&nbsp; 25% SXR8 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 15% EUNL &nbsp;|&nbsp; 10% Cash
          </div>
          <div class="quote">
            <span class="quote-text">I prefer UCITS ETFs for tax efficiency here in Germany. DEGIRO's low costs on European exchanges make it the perfect fit for my strategy.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="disclaimer-wrapper">
      <div class="disclaimer">
        <strong>Note:</strong> These profiles use demo data for illustration purposes. Names, countries, professions, and quotes are representative examples based on common international investor scenarios. Real verified profiles are coming soon. Investment amounts and allocations are for informational purposes only and do not constitute advice.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  :root {
    --bg-primary: #0f172a;
    --bg-secondary: #1e293b;
    --bg-card: #1a2332;
    --border: #334155;
    --text-primary: #f1f5f9;
    --text-secondary: #cbd5e1;
    --text-muted: #94a3b8;
    --accent: #D4B95A;
    --accent-hover: #d4b55a;
    --accent-bg: rgba(212, 185, 90, 0.08);
    --accent-border: rgba(212, 185, 90, 0.25);
    --green: #22c55e;
    --green-bg: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.08);
    --blue-accent: #60a5fa;
    --blue-bg: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.08);
    --purple: #a78bfa;
    --purple-bg: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.08);
    --orange: #fb923c;
    --orange-bg: rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.08);
    --pink: #f472b6;
    --pink-bg: rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.08);
    --teal: #2dd4bf;
    --teal-bg: rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.08);
    --shadow-lg: 0 12px 40px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    --shadow-card: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    --radius-xl: 20px;
    --radius-lg: 16px;
    --radius-md: 12px;
    --radius-sm: 8px;
  }

  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .investor-profiles-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 24px auto 0;
  }

  .header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .header .icon-circle {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent-bg);
    border: 2px solid var(--accent-border);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .header .icon-circle svg {
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .header h1 {
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .header h1 span {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .header p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 10px;
  }

  .demo-notice {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--accent-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-border);
    border-radius: 50px;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .demo-notice .dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    animation: pulse-dot 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-dot {
    0%,
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.4;
      transform: scale(1.6);
    }
  }

  .profiles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .profile-card {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 24px 22px;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .profile-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
  }

  .profile-card.accent-green::before { background: var(--green); }
  .profile-card.accent-blue::before { background: var(--blue-accent); }
  .profile-card.accent-purple::before { background: var(--purple); }
  .profile-card.accent-orange::before { background: var(--orange); }
  .profile-card.accent-pink::before { background: var(--pink); }
  .profile-card.accent-teal::before { background: var(--teal); }

  .profile-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--accent-border);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .profile-card .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .profile-card .flag-emoji {
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .profile-card .name-block {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .profile-card .name {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .profile-card .meta {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .profile-card .meta .separator {
    color: var(--border);
  }

  .profile-card .info-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.4);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .profile-card .info-row:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .profile-card .info-label {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .profile-card .info-value {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: right;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .profile-card .info-value.highlight {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .profile-card .allocation {
    margin-top: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .profile-card .allocation strong {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .profile-card .quote {
    margin-top: auto;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    background: var(--accent-bg);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    position: relative;
  }

  .profile-card .quote::before {
    content: '\201C';
    position: absolute;
    top: -6px;
    left: 8px;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.5;
    line-height: 1;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .profile-card .quote-text {
    padding-top: 6px;
  }

  .disclaimer-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 20px auto 24px;
  }

  .disclaimer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .profiles-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .profiles-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .investor-profiles-container {
      padding: 0 4px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .profile-card {
      padding: 18px 16px;
    }
  }
</style>

